{
  "stem": "10960.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I should advertise maybe, you know, to look for him, just as an appreciation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] I am alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he said, this woman-- I married this wife mine who was born in the Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as the trucks were waiting-- I'm going back to the trucks now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she decided to take the baby and go back because she was positive that it will be of war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- he received for drafting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she knew that he will be going to the-- to the army, so she went back-- she went back on those trucks home to Russia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He doesn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Geller, you know, in Russia, your-- your wife could-- name could be Geller.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My name is [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Milevski. ?] Well, I can have my-- my passport and I can still be-- is written, the name of your wife?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, no, there is no names, just a wife and a child, which is-- So I said you know that I have a feeling that I am in your hands.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can save two lives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My husband is now in Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's a good man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Could be that your wife is asking for help from my husband.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Can you imagine that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would never dream that I would be standing in front of a man to ask to help me, to save my life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, I get chills, but I have to go to ask my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His mother was living with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll go with you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The child was there with my, you know, landlady when I left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was before, and she was living in the main street, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
